Package: chronofeat
Type: Package
Title: Time-Based Feature Engineering for Forecasting
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R:
    person("Resul", "Akay", , "resul.akay@quantics.io", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A flexible, formula-based interface for time series feature engineering
    and forecasting. Automatically generates temporal features (lags, moving averages,
    rolling statistics, calendar features) from a concise formula specification.
    Model-agnostic: works with any R model that accepts a fit/predict interface.
    Supports multi-group panel data and recursive multi-step prediction.
